channel.title: Jaws Unleashed
channel.description:
I remember playing this game a long time ago, I didn't own it but this was in the time I use to rent games out for a week or so and save up on monthly vouches. Just making this topic because I'm am about to download it and play for the first time since PS2, woo!
BIG deal? Yeah it's a big deal, its a game of its own kind. Basically you're a shark and you do shark things, eat and that is literally about it but it's somehow fun. You eat smaller sharks, people, boats etc.
Anyone else played it before? Surely you have.
